Health Care REIT Agrees to Buy Genesis Real Estate Assets for $2.4 Billion

-- B y   S t e v e n   F r o m m
-- 
2011-02-28T21:02:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/health-care-reit-agrees-to-buy-genesis-real-estate-assets-for-2-4-billion.html
  Health Care REIT Inc . said it has
signed a definitive agreement to acquire substantially all of
the real estate assets of privately-owned Genesis HealthCare, a
leading provider of short-term post-acute, rehabilitation,
assisted living and long-term care services, for a purchase
price of $2.4 billion.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven Fromm at 
 sfromm@bloomberg.net  